            <h1>🛸 Introduction</h1>
            <div class="quote">"Your beliefs become your thoughts… Your thoughts become your words… Your words become your actions… Your actions become your habits… Your habits become your values… Your values become your destiny." <br /> — Mahatma Gandhi</div>
            <p>Welcome to your <b>3D Personal Playbook</b>. This assessment is a snapshot of your starting point.</p>
                        
            <div><br />📖 <b>Overview</b><br /><br />
            This workbook is designed to help you strive to thrive by examining the three essential dimensions of a fulfilling life: <b>Body, Mind, and Spirit.</b>
            <br /><br />Most development programs focus on only one area—like career or fitness. The 3D approach recognizes that these dimensions are interconnected. A healthy body supports a sharp mind, and a clear mind creates the space for a resilient spirit. By assessing where you are today, you can build a roadmap that aligns your daily actions with your God-given purpose.           
           </div>
           <br />
           
