<br />For Example on part 2, here are some core values to help you:
<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Spirituality: Faith, Inner Peace, Mindfulness, Connection.
<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Character: Integrity, Courage, Honesty, Humility.
<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Relational: Compassion, Service, Loyalty, Forgiveness.
<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Growth: Curiosity, Discipline, Wisdom, Resilience.
</label>
